<A>__{kirk races }
<L>__{interior enterprise engine room}
<A>__{kirk emerges to encounter scotty and bones. their looks tell him. he sees the flashing light over the reactor room. he dashes for the control panel. bones grabs him.}
<C>__{scotty}
<D>__{no, sir! you'll flood the whole compartment...!}
<C>__{kirk}
<D>__{he'll die !}
