<D>__{he's dead already, jim.}
<A>__{kirk's eyes bulge.}
<C>__{kirk}
<D>__{oh, god.}
<B>__{angle at reactor room glass door}
<A>__{with stunned understanding, kirk stumbles to the door, sees spock on his knees, hands blackened, face cracked with radiation lines and scars. spock shakes his head. with a feeble hand he reaches the intercom button: filtered communication.}
