<D>__{don't grieve, admiral it's logical: the good of the many outweighs }
<A>__{he almost keels over. kirk has tears streaming down his face.}
<C>__{kirk}
<D>__{... the good of the few...}
<C>__{spock}
<D>__{or the one.}
<A>__{he props a hand on the glass to support himself. kirk's hand reflexively goes to match spock's on the other side of the glass }
<C>__{spock}
